<BaseLayout title="About — AI Copyright Legal" description="About AI Copyright Legal — who we are, our mission, and our editorial standards.">
  <article class="acl-legal">
    <div class="acl-legal-container">
      <h1>About AI Copyright Legal</h1>

      <p class="text-lg" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;">
        AI Copyright Legal is an independent resource dedicated to helping creators, businesses, and developers navigate the rapidly evolving intersection of artificial intelligence and copyright law.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We believe everyone deserves clear, accessible information about how AI affects their creative rights and legal obligations. Whether you're an artist whose work was scraped to train AI, a business using AI to create content, or a developer building AI tools — we're here to help you understand the law.</p>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Breaking news</strong> — Court rulings, settlements, and regulatory changes</li>
        <li><strong>In-depth guides</strong> — Practical explainers on AI copyright topics</li>
        <li><strong>Lawsuit tracker</strong> — Every major AI copyright case, tracked and analyzed</li>
        <li><strong>International law</strong> — How different countries handle AI copyright</li>
        <li><strong>Free tools</strong> — Practical tools for compliance and protection</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Editorial Standards</h2>
      <p>We are committed to accuracy, fairness, and transparency:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Primary sources</strong> — We cite court documents, government reports, and official statements</li>
        <li><strong>Both sides</strong> — We cover perspectives of both creators and AI companies</li>
        <li><strong>Not legal advice</strong> — We clearly state that our content is informational, not legal counsel</li>
        <li><strong>Corrections</strong> — We promptly correct errors and note updates</li>
        <li><strong>AI disclosure</strong> — We use AI tools to assist with research and drafting. All content is reviewed, fact-checked, and edited by humans</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>AI Use Disclosure</h2>
      <p>In the spirit of the transparency we advocate, we disclose that AI Copyright Legal uses AI tools in our editorial process:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI assists with research, initial drafts, and content structuring</li>
        <li>All content is reviewed, fact-checked, and substantially edited by human editors</li>
        <li>Our interactive tools are built with standard web technologies</li>
        <li>We do not publish purely AI-generated content without human editorial oversight</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>We'd love to hear from you:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>General inquiries:</strong> hello@aicopyrightlegal.com</li>
        <li><strong>Press & media:</strong> press@aicopyrightlegal.com</li>
        <li><strong>Legal/privacy:</strong> privacy@aicopyrightlegal.com</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
